data.text:
Abhijit Name Popularity

At NamesLook, the name Abhijit is recorded 3,862 times globally, ranking it as the 12,415th most common name worldwide.

Abhijit is most prevalent in India, with 2,265 occurrences, making it the 315th most popular name in the country.
